Use the standard library
This is how to is_happy of s:
   When s's length is less than 4, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that seen is []
   Do this s's length times:
      Remember that ch is item i in s
      When ch is in seen, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Add seen to ch
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
